    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它来自天上</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >东京的未来看似光明——直到奇怪的发现将两条生命拉入未知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你扮演的是充满好奇心的高中生丽，她与神秘的科学家澪相遇。最初的偶遇逐渐演变成更宏大的故事：城市地下埋藏的秘密、星空中书写的疑问，以及一个无人能忽视的倒计时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们将携手探寻真相——穿越悬念、危险和脆弱的信任。每前进一步，你们都离希望……或灾难更近一步。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172750/extras/e360d81a74ecfb9a86d1235ce9110e3c.avif?t=1758145747\" width=1280 height=716 /></span>游戏概述</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《它来自天上》将你带入充满悬念的未来东京，天界威胁的阴影日益逼近。随着丽和澪的人生交织，你将揭开隐藏的真相，直面危险，体验一个时刻都令人感到紧迫的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引人入胜的故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开线性、紧密交织的叙事，融合了悬念、神秘和人类情感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >惊艳的视觉效果</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >富有表现力的角色和细节丰富的背景，将东京的街道、天空和秘密栩栩如生地展现出来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >互动式游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速反应事件和沉浸式场景让你沉浸在紧张刺激的场景中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人难忘的角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >澪、丽以及他们周围的人物都经过精心塑造——每个人都带着缺陷、梦想和挣扎，引发你的共鸣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动人心弦的配乐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心创作的配乐增强了每个场景的亲密感、紧迫感和戏剧性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式视觉小说体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >叙事核心：完整的线性故事，引人入胜，从头到尾引人入胜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断演变的羁绊：随着事件的展开，见证人际关系的演变和发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >视觉沉浸：艺术作品捕捉了东京的活力与弥漫的不安感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《它来自我们之上》是一部以故事为主导的视觉小说，讲述了秘密、牺牲以及奇迹与灾难之间微妙的界限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172750/extras/928fa643f906e49131f601f8f1dbbd2e.avif?t=1758145747\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172750/extras/75a9c892428b26033efdb31f7cd9e2c2.avif?t=1758145747\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172750/extras/bc6e2285a8068f46551fc55e0dd1dde3.avif?t=1758145747\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172750/extras/419ed470a1a4a972c756ad28a74ec2bf.avif?t=1758145747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172750/extras_big/419ed470a1a4a972c756ad28a74ec2bf.avif?t=1758145747 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172750/extras/5960fe5b99d7fbfd631b65cc84359527.avif?t=1758145747\" width=1196 height=674 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172750/extras/9e6d5b0b24186fe2d1de0428f31e5194.avif?t=1758145747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172750/extras_big/9e6d5b0b24186fe2d1de0428f31e5194.avif?t=1758145747 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
